{"tid":1961594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共 : 國際社會應按照共產黨方式解讀《基本法》","createTime":"2020-04-07T01:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T01:47:32.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb4bca1d6a085b993debda521f1af17d08b7ddb","tid":1961594,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"謝鋒：國際社會應全面準確理解及真心實意支持落實基本法<br />\n07.04.2020 05:20<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署特派員謝鋒通過視頻接受瑞士、沙特阿拉伯、泰國、多米尼加及巴基斯坦新任駐港總領事到任拜會。他指回歸23年來，香港社會出現各種紛爭，往往與沒有全面準確理解基本法有關。特别是反中亂港勢力内外勾結，刻意歪曲基本法宗旨。謝鋒說，國際社會應全面準確理解，以及真心實意支持落實基本法，確保一國兩制行穩致遠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279171&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279171%26csid%3D261_341&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=a7a4b58e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279171&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7569b359b8710a8a929efcb343a7e06d78f31c78","tid":1961594,"uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:45:54.000Z","msg":"國際要聽你講？大家咁高咁大"},{"pid":"5f17d8dc3f5000731ebfb09e07cf2d5bb2cca218","tid":1961594,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"行穩致遠?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">含撚致軟咋掛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e42aacb17c3aad153fc0b459bc10f65eb74976b","tid":1961594,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:46:44.000Z","msg":"白皮書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e49e7b9faf2bd70d7fd5c91f081dcc9e563d51","tid":1961594,"uid":187987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"屌你，一係就寫過哂成份基本法。<br />\n個個人都係照字面解讀，你就要用共產黨思想解讀<img src=\"/assets